<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٤١٥ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3">آدَمُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/2779">شُعْبَةُ </a>قَالَ: حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/5183">قَتَادَةُ </a>قَالَ: سَمِعْتُ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">أَنَسَ بْنَ مَالِكٍ </a>قَالَ: قَالَ النَّبِيُّ <span class="special">ﷺ</span>: <span class="c2">«الْبُزَاقُ فِي الْمَسْجِدِ خَطِيئَةٌ، وَكَفَّارَتُهَا دَفْنُهَا»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>